---
title: Smart Tofu and Dal with Frizzled Shallots
description: Tonight's dinner is warming, comforting and deliciously wholesome. Tofu is seared in our Dal Spice Blend, then baked to perfection before being added to a creamy dal curry. A generous sprinkling of frizzled shallots adds texture and so much flavour!

